comments.content: The image is so small, I can’t even see it.

Something appears to have gone wrong with embedding the image -- its filename contains [..] characters, which clash with the square bracketed formatting codes.

 ![](http://web.archive.org/web/20131011025540im_/http:/typophile.com/files/e06823f9340232664a54e55b27d21083_6404_4206_3523.png)
